　　15　　日\r\n　　　　                      書  記  官  葉竹芸","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/NHEM/110%2c%e6%b9%96%e7%b0%a1%2c403%2c20220128%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"NHEM,110,湖簡,403,20220128,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"湖簡","JNO":"403","JDATE":"20220128","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}